The paper discusses reputation systems, which are commonly used in the field of computer security (cs.CR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also proposes a new discounting operator for Subjective Logic, which is a probabilistic model commonly used in social networks and information retrieval (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the handling of trust networks, which is a topic in data structures (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.LG).
